728308f-a.title: Richmond: Amboy Road - Maguire Avenue
728308f-a.text:
6056 and 6058 amboy Rowd, south side, adjoining
(to the east) Maguire Avenue. No. 6056 is the Citzens'
Engine Company No. 1,part of which is occupied by the Princes
Bay Station of the New York Public Library.
1923
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
